      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "This allows axes that span two columns (or rows) that are offset     from one another to have the same size."
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": "fig = plt.figure(constrained_layout=True)         axs = fig.subplot_mosaic(\"AAAB"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "blockquote"
            }
          ],
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "CCDD\")"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "Without this routine, the axes D will be wider than C, because the     margin width between the two columns in C has no width by default,     whereas the margins between the two columns of D are set by the     width of the margin between A and B. However, obviously the user would     like C and D to be the same size, so we need to add constraints to these     \"submerged\" margins."
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "This routine makes all the interior margins the same, and the spacing     between the three columns in A and the two column in C are all set to the     margins between the two columns of D."
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "See test_constrained_layout::test_constrained_layout12 for an example."
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "type": "blockquote"
        }
      ],
